> >What do you want 30-50 Amps for??? That would be 360 - 600 Watts. Even
> >if you go with 100 Watt high beams, 20 Amps should be plenty. The higher
> >your fuse is rated, the more likely you are to cause damage to your
> >wiring before it blows.
